snippet.title: A Day In The Life Of A Freelance Programmer (on vacation)
snippet.description:
A Day In The Life Of A Freelance Programmer (on vacation)

"Clean Code Friday"
If you want to receive one short email from me every week, where I go through a few of the most useful things I have explored and discovered this week. Things like; favourite apps, articles, podcasts, books, coding tips and tricks. Then feel free to join https://kalletech.com/clean-code-friday/

I also have a similar video called a day in the life of a software engineer that might be interesting for you if you liked this one.
There's not a lot of coding so if you came for that then I am sorry but the aim of the video was to show sort of what the lifestyle looks like for me when I am on vacation and how I am able to integrate my work into my holidays.
Hope you like it! :)

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
CONTACT: halldenkalle@gmail.com

INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/kallehallden/

DRONE: DJI Mavic Air - https://amzn.to/2NqkQa1

Secondary Lens: Panasonic 25mm - https://amzn.to/2UcTA1e

Secondary Lens: Olympus 45mm - https://amzn.to/2Ebp5SV

Zoom Lens: Panasonic 100-300mm - https://amzn.to/2U3UH3j

Monitor: AOC 27” - https://amzn.to/2U6hF9Z
